# Tests — OSS-01 SchemeEligibilityOracle

> Using Oss01 as T

### Import — AC-09 punktafgiftsvarer

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestImportExcisable:
  oss01 scope T.SchemeEligibilityOracle

scope TestImportExcisable:
  definition oss01.supply_type equals T.SupplyType.ImportGoods
  definition oss01.excisable equals true
  definition oss01.shipment_value_known equals true
  definition oss01.shipment_value_eur equals 100.0
  definition oss01.has_eu_seat equals false
  definition oss01.has_fixed_establishment_in_eu equals false
  definition oss01.consumption_is_other equals false
  definition oss01.consumption_equals_seat_country equals false
  definition oss01.via_electronic_interface equals false
  assertion oss01.outcome = T.SchemeOutcome.ImportExcludedExcisable
```

### Import — AC-07 værdi over 150 EUR

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestImportOver150:
  oss01 scope T.SchemeEligibilityOracle

scope TestImportOver150:
  definition oss01.supply_type equals T.SupplyType.ImportGoods
  definition oss01.excisable equals false
  definition oss01.shipment_value_known equals true
  definition oss01.shipment_value_eur equals 151.0
  definition oss01.has_eu_seat equals false
  definition oss01.has_fixed_establishment_in_eu equals false
  definition oss01.consumption_is_other equals false
  definition oss01.consumption_equals_seat_country equals false
  definition oss01.via_electronic_interface equals false
  assertion oss01.outcome = T.SchemeOutcome.ImportExcludedValueTooHigh
```

### Import — AC-06/08 inden for eller lig 150 EUR

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestImportEligible150:
  oss01 scope T.SchemeEligibilityOracle

scope TestImportEligible150:
  definition oss01.supply_type equals T.SupplyType.ImportGoods
  definition oss01.excisable equals false
  definition oss01.shipment_value_known equals true
  definition oss01.shipment_value_eur equals 150.0
  definition oss01.has_eu_seat equals false
  definition oss01.has_fixed_establishment_in_eu equals false
  definition oss01.consumption_is_other equals false
  definition oss01.consumption_equals_seat_country equals false
  definition oss01.via_electronic_interface equals false
  assertion oss01.outcome = T.SchemeOutcome.ImportScheme
```

### Ikke-EU — AC-01 ydelser, intet EU-hjemsted eller FE

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestNonEuServices:
  oss01 scope T.SchemeEligibilityOracle

scope TestNonEuServices:
  definition oss01.supply_type equals T.SupplyType.Services
  definition oss01.has_eu_seat equals false
  definition oss01.has_fixed_establishment_in_eu equals false
  definition oss01.consumption_is_other equals false
  definition oss01.consumption_equals_seat_country equals false
  definition oss01.excisable equals false
  definition oss01.shipment_value_known equals false
  definition oss01.shipment_value_eur equals 0.0
  definition oss01.via_electronic_interface equals false
  assertion oss01.outcome = T.SchemeOutcome.NonEuScheme
```

### EU — AC-05 samme land som forbrugssted

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestEuSameCountryNoOss:
  oss01 scope T.SchemeEligibilityOracle

scope TestEuSameCountryNoOss:
  definition oss01.supply_type equals T.SupplyType.Services
  definition oss01.has_eu_seat equals true
  definition oss01.has_fixed_establishment_in_eu equals false
  definition oss01.consumption_is_other equals false
  definition oss01.consumption_equals_seat_country equals true
  definition oss01.excisable equals false
  definition oss01.shipment_value_known equals false
  definition oss01.shipment_value_eur equals 0.0
  definition oss01.via_electronic_interface equals false
  assertion oss01.outcome = T.SchemeOutcome.NoOssSchemeSameCountry
```
